description:
Easy Vegan Dinners!

Eating vegan has never been easier! Your favorite dinner recipes...now veganized. With chapters on go-to pasta, curries and stir fries, tacos, and healthy bowls, and MORE you'll find 30 dinner recipes that will make your whole family say "YES"!

In addition to the recipes, this ebook is filled with all the tools you will need to start veganizing your favorite recipes right at home.

Read more about Easy Vegan Dinners here.
name: Easy Vegan Dinners
